  "install_text": "Built for multi-year, zero-maintenance deployments, the Lansitec Cat-1 Macro Tracker fuses dual-constellation GNSS, BLE 5.0 scanning and LTE Cat-1 connectivity inside a rugged IP66 enclosure. A massive 38 000 mAh Li-SOCl2 battery powers up to 7 years of adaptive reporting, while edge-side filters, offline caching and motion-driven autonomy turn raw pings into actionable asset intelligence—no external power, no data waste.",
